{"tid":1827590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逼自己做左一日港豬/ 一日駝鳥，原來係好辛苦","createTime":"2020-01-17T05:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T05:30:29.000Z","uid":57012,"like":29,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a696d9f0062ae2991aa04c0d5a918ba6d22fdf","tid":1827590,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"明明大家都知道，都有預知到運動一停落黎或者係冷卻既<br />\n<br />\n時候就會開始大清算。日日都有手足都會上門比狗咬，點<br />\n<br />\n解仲可以講完個嬲字就繼續正常咁生活。<br />\n<br />\n你地問心個句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">為呢場運動付出左幾多</span><br />\n<br />\n唔洗答我或者其他人，答自己就得架啦<br />\n<br />\n我自己做左個實驗，尋日出左街，盡量唔比自己接觸呢類<br />\n<br />\n型既新聞/ 消息。一開始個陣都ok，因為真係太耐無咁放鬆去下<br />\n<br />\n街，睇下嘢。但係當過左一陣之後發覺真係唔得。個心<br />\n<br />\n好辛苦，原來當你全程投入過既時候，你係好難抽到身出<br />\n<br />\n黎。<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n希望大家要堅持，如果唔係，好現實好殘忍咁講一句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">拉下拉下，就無曬架啦</span>"},{"pid":"0b369c4f385e07c5642720c34cc4877acf364a8b","tid":1827590,"uid":57012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWpDYHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWpDYHQ.jpg&h=2ae73b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zv9P5nR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzv9P5nR.jpg&h=8bb1481f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42049383b03bc1b1051a4b2ab7596c6f18b2d457","tid":1827590,"uid":57012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:21:18.000Z","msg":"咁多無可疑，你真係信？你真係睇到麻目左？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2667Bs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2667Bs.jpg&h=5ac5ad5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mBkDegt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBkDegt.jpg&h=abcf7112&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d640fd85ecbe2217e80f326f9a5d52afe2e3cca","tid":1827590,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"